<div class="second-page-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <h2>"Preserving the cultural heritage of weaving that has existed since the era of the Panjalu Kingdom of Kediri until now"</h2>
        <div class="main-button"><a href="shop_en">Collection</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="visit-country">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-9">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>About Us</h2>
          <p>Located on the suburb of Kediri City, precisely on Jl. KH. Agus Salim Gang 11 No 12 B, RT 03 RW 07, Bandar Kidul Village, 63118. Kampung Wisata Tenun Ikat Bandar Kidul has a long history starting several generations ago since 1950. Founded by dedicated weaving craftsmen, this village symbolizes perseverance, skill, and love for the art of Tenun Ikat.</p>
          <p>Tenun Ikat Bandar Kidul is famous for its intricate and beautiful motifs, each with its own meaning and story. To this day, craftsmen continue to maintain the traditional techniques taught by their ancestors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>Vision</h2>
          <p>To make the Kampung Wisata Tenun Ikat Bandar Kidul a superior cultural tourism destination known nationally and internationally and a centre for Tenun Ikat education and training.</p>
          <h2>Mission</h2>
          <p>•	Preserving and developing the art of traditional Tenun Ikat.</p>
          <p>•	Improving community welfare through tourism and the creative economy.</p>
          <p>•	Educate the younger generation about the importance of preserving and continuing cultural heritage.</p>
          <p>Through the tourist village program, we are proud to preserve and introduce this cultural heritage to the world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reservation-form">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div id="map">
              <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eutGHvx5ax0?si=0" width="100%" height="450px" frameborder="0" style="border:0; border-top-left-radius: 23px; border-top-right-radius: 23px; border-bottom-left-radius: 23px; border-bottom-right-radius: 23px;" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="cities-town">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="slider-content">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h2 style="color: #572f4a;"><em>Desa Tenun</em> Documentation</h2>
              </div>
              {{#each gallery}}
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="owl-cites-town owl-carousel">
                  <div class="item">
                    <div class="thumb">
                      <img src="./assets/images/{{this.dataValues.image}}" alt="">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              {{/each}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="weekly-offers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3">
